  "title": "Valid Argument Form",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "An argument form with premises \\(\\Gamma\\) and conclusion \\(\\varphi\\) is\n\\emph{valid} if every truth assignment that satisfies every formula in\n\\(\\Gamma\\) also satisfies \\(\\varphi\\).",
